data.description: Wow! Absolutely must see this immaculate rancher in a cozy neighborhood tucked right in the heart of the Valley, in a quiet cul-de-sac, with a fully fenced backyard! Enjoy all the benefits of a quiet neighborhood, with incredibly easy access to Pines, Sprague, and the freeway! Enjoy the spacious great room style living area with a fireplace and the wonderful master bedroom with double sinks and a great walk-in closet! Bonus office space is built into the garage and everything is all on one level! Lots of natural light with big windows and skylights! Everything is ready for you!
